data.description: Modern updates and move in ready!  This charming home features large family room open to kitchen and dining area.  2 split bedrooms and updated bathroom.  Pretty, wood look, easy to maintain vinyl flooring!  SS appliances, with pretty fixtures.  Corner lot with huge backyard and big deck for hanging out and grilling!  Just around the corner from convenience store, gas and grocery!  Short drive to elementary school in Tom Bean.  Call today to schedule a home visit, just 30 minutes notice.  Tenant occupied but no lease.
